  "special": {
    "title": "Thinking outside the box.",
    "description": "Red text: Thinking outside the box.\n\nWhile aiming down sights, it fires a 7-round burst. Grants bonus critical hit damage with multiplicative scaling, plus higher base damage and magazine size. Always rolls with a Tediore grip."
  },
  "notes": "Opening the weapon's container triggers an ECHO message from Handsome Jack: \"Aw, what's in the box?!\".\nThe line is tied to opening the container and can still play after completing The Talon of God.\nThe container also holds a woman's skull.\nA copy can spawn each time you enter The Dust. If left uncollected, leaving and re-entering reshuffles its location; quitting to menu and loading back in spawns a fresh copy, replacing any unclaimed one.\nBelow Ultimate Vault Hunter Mode, its level is set by the host's current story mission level, not The Dust's area level.",
